28 (a1) Hearing. – If a person fails or refuses to provide to the Auditor or the Auditor's
29 authorized representatives the access described in subsection (a) of this section, the Auditor may
30 commence an action in superior court for a show cause hearing. The person shall appear at the
31 hearing and show cause why the person failed or refused to comply with subsection (a) of this
32 section. The court may issue an injunction to the person to comply with subsection (a) of this
33 section.
